replies.body:
Maybe Astro-Poro looks confused for a moment, but then giddy as he notices a spiral galaxy that reminds him of a poro snack? {{item:2052}} 

Gentleman poro's chair could fall backwards and let him tumble off unhurt, instead of being squished? 

Just some suggestions that maximize the adorable charm of poros, without fear of making the wee little guys too sad. :) {{item:2043}}
